Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在脸朝下地浮在一座游泳池里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here I am floating face-down in a swimming pool
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想有座泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wanted a pool
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后  我也拥有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and in the end, I got one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是如何走到这地步的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did I get here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.80,0:01:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都要从昨天说起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it all started yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.57,0:01:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.28,0:01:31.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:31.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.16,0:01:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你刚刚有说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, did you say something?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么要在你院子里挖坑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you digging up your yard?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在挖泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm putting in a pool
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pool?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我要邀请我最爱的隔壁邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to invite my favorite next-door neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖完了就来一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as soon as it's ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.71,0:01:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.83,0:02:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不进去你的细菌滋生的大泥坑里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be caught dead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in your muddy, little bacteria hole
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.77,0:02:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只游高级的泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only swim in sophisticated pools
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你反悔想进来游的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you change your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.37,0:02:07.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池就快挖好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:07.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's almost done
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.02,0:02:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's done
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.85,0:02:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.65,0:02:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么他就能有泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does he get to have a pool?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有资格拥有泳池的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anyone around here deserves a pool
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.99,0:02:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快进泳池里跟我们一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, come join us in the pool
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.45,0:02:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  趁水还湿着进来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, while the water's still wet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,池子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘了泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the pool
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.82,0:03:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,池子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,池子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.81,0:03:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静点  泡消毒泳池水的大烂泥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet, you chlorinated clods
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还游什么潮得要死的泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs a soggy, old pool
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.99,0:03:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明都有高贵无比的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you have the luxury and elegance
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,室内空调可以吹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of indoor air conditioning
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.27,0:03:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a little hot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.61,0:03:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,池子太酷了  痴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is one cool pool, my fool
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路游泳平安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Swim safely, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meet you at the pool
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so hot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要怂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be a drip
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来游
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a dip
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定很想进来游
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know you want to
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点游个泳凉快一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just take a quick dip to cool off
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That a boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump in
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,池子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王  没人听到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune nobody heard me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  放过海兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you leave those sea bunnies alone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and come to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.42,0:05:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我能一个人独占泳池了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can have the pool all to myself
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,池子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, pool
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ciao, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.89,0:05:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ciao, Squidwardo
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.48,0:05:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  一定要给我们来吹个竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidwardo, you must play your clarinet for us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,务必来一首
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You simply must
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  美人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ciao bella
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋  我一定是睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Egad, I must've fallen asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让他们发现我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't let them find me here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要玩水了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get wet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池玩具在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the pool toys?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别进泳池小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the pool shed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都放在泳池小屋里了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're in the pool shed, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta hide
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me first
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先来挑玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can pick first
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪个玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which toy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挑我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就挑这个又大又丑的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take this big, ugly one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,软塌塌的  浮不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too floppy to float on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要充个气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It needs more air
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that ought to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挑得不错  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice find, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮来坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannon sit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池大战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool fight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池大战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool fight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池大战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pool fight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pool--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's broken
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乘风破浪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ride the wave
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乘风破浪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ride the wave
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向后拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tug it back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向前拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tug it forth
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向后拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tug it back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向前拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tug it forth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Black hole
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again, again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是泳池玩具  两个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was the pool toy, you idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最神奇的魔术了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's the greatest magic trick I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  再变一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I admit it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没经过你同意就在你泳池里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used your pool without permission
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.57,0:09:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我特别嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I'm really jealous of it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要你的泳池椅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want your pool chairs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要你的泳池喷气口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want your pool jets
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要你的泳池浮条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want your pool noodles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.52,0:09:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我最想要的就是这个跳水板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And most of all, I want this diving board
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我们是最棒的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, we're best neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你随时都可以来我泳池里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can use my pool anytime you like
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白天晚上都行  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,day or night, you silly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想不想来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, how'd you like to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上小板板来跳水水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take a divey-wivey on the boardy-woardy, hmm?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免了  就先不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, thanks, but I just couldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你务必要来跳水  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, you must take a dive, Squidwardo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就来跳水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would love to take a dive
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我高中可是加了游泳队的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was on my high school swim team
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  这架梯子可以调
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, this ladder is adjustable
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要调高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go higher?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也爱你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you all too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  那就当你要调高了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take that as a yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调高吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crank it up, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  美人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ciao bella
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I dive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Troppo elevato
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.67,0:10:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太高了  太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too high, too high
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太高了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too high, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调低点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crank it down
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美一跳  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect dive, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.08,0:11:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是我便走到了这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's how I got here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.16,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFAF&}高伯教父
