Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(524,388)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的餐好了  海霸王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your order is ready, Mr. Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've mingled Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,混进了我的海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in my kelp shake
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我帮你再打一杯奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, let me refresh that for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold your seahorses
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西既油腻  又清凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's greasy, yet cool and refreshing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上再给我来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fetch me another posthaste
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖相好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That does look good
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want one too
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感应到了赚钱的良机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sense a money-tunity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:26.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1302,258)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新蟹堡冰奶油  正在供应中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The brand-new Patty Whip is now on the menu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1588,482)}蟹堡冰奶油
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,适度付点巨款即可购买
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,available for a moderately exorbitant upcharge
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能点两份打包外带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get two to-go?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份打包外带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two to-go please
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲多做蟹堡冰奶油  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep those Patty Whips coming, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在加把劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:49.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,614)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closing time
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再过来  吃到你动脉硬化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can harden your arteries tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're closed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高伯教父想要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Goobfather would like to have
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们老板谈个话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a little talk with your boss
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高伯教父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goobfather?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是高菲高伯的经理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the manager of the Goofy Goober?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是我的正职
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just my day job
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高伯教父才是我的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Goobfather is my true identity
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我控制着全裤头村的冰淇淋贸易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I control all the ice cream trade in this town
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.86,0:13:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还听说了你家在卖泄堡病油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I heard about your little fatty flips
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(798,576)}蟹堡冰奶油
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹堡冰奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Patty Whips
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点点良性竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a little friendly competition
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never hurt anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你们还是只做蟹黄堡比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but maybe you should stick to flipping patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷饮业务就交给专家  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave the frozen treats to the experts, hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.08,0:13:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我新找到的摇钱树不能就这么断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna stop selling my newest moneymaker
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小的们  动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do your stuff, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈  我想唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama, I want to sing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得谢谢我没让你变冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be thankful I didn't turn you into gelato
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, boss
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖不了蟹堡冰奶油了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Patty Whips
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, boyo
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的餐厅我做主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.66,0:14:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我能决定蟹堡王该卖什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no one tells me what's on me menu but me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡冰奶油机  又重新启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Patty Whip machine, is working again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整晚都在重建这个机器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spent all night rebuilding it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡冰奶油正式回归供应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty Whips are back on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.69,0:14:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是高伯教父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what if the Goobfather
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带着高伯暴徒手下回来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his goober goons come back?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给蟹堡王加了点安保措施
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought in a little protection meself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出来吧  小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on out, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是不是有点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't they a little, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,elderly?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们皱纹可能是多了点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We may be a little wrinkly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们身体还硬朗着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we're as tough as jerky
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're dead
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高伯教父想再找你们谈个话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Goobfather would like to have another little talk
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是那位不听话的螃蟹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't the crab who don't listen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再教训教训他  小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teach him another lesson, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急  高伯教父
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Goobfather
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那些来捣乱的扔出蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Throw these interloper out of me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始排成42号阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Initiate formation 42
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边是不是有指虎大促销
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that a sale on brass knuckles?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,指虎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brass knuckles?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有适合我的尺寸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do they have my size?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to skedaddle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这俩暴徒身手不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These goons are good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被打成奶油了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're whipped
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次招几个壮一点的打手  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time you hire some muscle, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得有肌肉的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make sure they have muscles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃花生吧  傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat goobers, you goofballs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都闹够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough of this bilge water
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去高伯教父的地盘亲手较量一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to take the fight to the Goobfater's home turf
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,580)}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.23,0:16:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找找破坏后能产生严重影响的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your eye open for anything worth sabotaging
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我两大球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a double scoop
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.65,0:16:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草漩涡  多加彩糖粒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of kelp swirl with extra sprinkles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.07,0:16:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两球海草漩涡  多加彩糖粒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double K swirl and make it snow
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就破坏那个调温器了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That thermostat, that'll do
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在得转移别人注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all we need is a distraction
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it handled
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.97,0:17:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check me out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so lame
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我就是目不转睛想看他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can't take my eyes off the guy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打心里感受到了他冰淇淋勺的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feel the rhythm of his scoops in my soul
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这段比较难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the tricky part
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样一定会让他们雪糕化掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll sizzle their sorbet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家跟上节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try and keep up, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的冰淇淋勺着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My scoops are on fire
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的勺子好有火热的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His funky scoops are so smokin' hot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都让我流汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sweating
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火热的不是勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not his spoons
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是有人把温度调高了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone's turned up the heat
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋会有严重安全隐患
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ice cream is going critical
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big finish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该逃出这家冰淇淋店了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to blow this ice cream stand
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁冰淇淋店还没炸赶紧跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before this ice cream stand blows
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该开溜了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to cheese it, boyo
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟老海军作对  有你好受的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mess with an old Navy man
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会逮到你的  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家海绵也照样逮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your little sponge too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be annihilated
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  高伯教父来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, it's the Goobfather
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竞争对手餐厅要撞上我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're about to be hit by a competing restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经做好反击准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're ready for 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,部署软冰淇淋炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deploy soft serve cannons
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激活太妃糖履带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Activate toffee treads
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热奶糖榴弹炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot fudge howitzer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启动引擎  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try the engines, boyo
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射冰淇淋炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire ice cream cannons
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正在发射冰淇淋炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Firing ice cream cannons
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,避开炮弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evasive maneuvers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开火反击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Return fire
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开冰淇淋反击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Return ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃我两大球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a double scoop
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑子冻住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brain freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃我热奶糖  坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat hot fudge, villain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼得又黏又美味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such sticky yet delicious pain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了撒彩糖粒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the sprinkles
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射甜筒无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Launch sugar cone drones
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.97,0:20:05.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你送进冰柜里  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:05.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sending you to the deep freeze, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做梦  高伯教父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In your ice dreams, Goobfather
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fudge
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not giving up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me neither
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋大王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Ice Cream King
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放下你们的第一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cease your hostil-lily--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hostile--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,quit fightin'
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋不能用来打架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream isn't meant for brawling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该为世界带来糖分搭建的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to bring sugar-built fun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.74,0:21:07.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让所有人肚子疼  冻脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:07.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,belly aches, and brain freezes to the world
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不该大打出手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't be fighting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有不少白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of saps--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者说  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or, customers in town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以由我们服务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for both of us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你们还要继续打下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you don't quit fighting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要使出我的终极武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll use my ultimate weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ice cream bomb
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream bomb?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've already stopped fighting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.06,0:21:32.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:32.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  我马上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'll be right down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bombs away
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来吃免费冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, free ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.22,0:22:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子都有免费冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free ice cream forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我们都被迫停业了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're all out of business
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来帮忙放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will someone please get me down?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.23,0:22:24.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:24.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
